episodes.title: Jehovah Witness Cult
episodes.description:
No matter what your belief is, you will want to give this Podcast on the Jehovah Witness religion a listen! 

JOIN us, on this Caution Podcast, where Tricia Interviews a former Jehovah Witness as she shares her personal experiences of being shunned and excommunicated  from the faith. Costing her the loss of most of her family and almost HER LIFE! 

Find out how Leticia found the strength to endure such trauma, how she overcame the odds and how she now dedicates her life to helping EXJW's!

This podcast offers insights into the emotional and psychological impact and abuse of this cult, what happens after a young female become pregnant out of wedlock and is put out by their family all in the name of  "religion" .

Find out what the process of rebuilding a new life outside of the faith entails and how to keep faith, love and light during it all!

STAY UNFILTERED! 
ALWAYS UNFILTERED!

Much Love,
Trish & Renee
